CNCP v1 23237
{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#13332: Bug in the invocation order of lifecycle hooks during component remounting/unmounting controlled via key",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:20:54.047943+00:00",
  "text": "Bug in the invocation order of lifecycle hooks during component remounting/unmounting controlled via key\n\n### Vue version\n\n3.5.14\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://play.vuejs.org/#\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n1.Open the browser console\n2.Click button\n3.Check the console output\n\n### What is expected?\n\nThe output order is: onBeforeUnmount -> onUnmounted -> onBeforeMount -> onMounted\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\nThe output order is: onBeforeUnmount -> onBeforeMount -> onUnmounted -> onMounted\n\n### System Info\n\n```shell\n\n```\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\n_No response_",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    "need guidance",
    ":hammer: p3-minor-bug"
  ],
